{
  "text": "There is the forty-five minute signal. Does Ra suggest a termination of this session, taking into consideration the instrument's condition and all the other conditions that we have placed on this? I am Ra. Information pertinent to this query has been previously covered. The choice of termination time, as you call it, is solely that of the questioner until the point at which we perceive the instrument beginning to use its vital resources due to the absence of transferred or native physical energy. The instrument remains open, as always.",
